original_title: Jean-Michel Jarre - Oxygene Live In Paris
overview: As part of the Oxygene 30th Anniversary Tour, Jean Michel Jarre performed 10 Oxygene concerts in Paris, from December 12 to December 26, 2007. The concerts took place at the Théâtre Marigny, a small, 1000 seats theater located in the Champs-Élysées.
title: Jean-Michel Jarre - Oxygene Live In Paris
